<br>
However I believe that I have used the Soapbox for its proper purpose: To keep people updated on the not-so-savory goings-on happening on our little server.<br>
<br>
But I also see that these topics in the soapbox, diverse and rancorous as they are, are the things that are IMPORTANT  to people;  Important enough to people that they momentarily ignore their substandard linguistic skills, their poor grammar, their atrocious spelling, and come right out and say what is on their mind, no matter how unintelligible it ends up being.<br>
<br>
That being said, it's hard to knock one topic while praising another.  This is the soapbox.  This is where you GO to say what you have to say, and to see what is being said.<br>
<br>
The poster who mentioned NOT reading it is right on the money.  I stopped reading the newspaper for just this reason: Too Damn Depressing.  So if it depresses me, I stop reading the Soapbox.  But then I find myself drawn back because I want to know what people care about.<br>
<br>
Just because I couldn't care less about the antics of FnF and Reso (Because I'm probably a good 3 to 6 months of constant play before I'll even SEE any of the realms they operate in, much less play in them) does not mean that others do not.<br>
<br>
We post here what is important to us.  Some of us thrive on misery and conflict, and it is evident as well.  Others of us thrive on change, which comes through conflict.  And still others of us like to sharpen our razor wit on someone else's rant.<br>
<br>
At least we HAVE a board like this to do it.  Other blue servers do not.  The Soapbox is, in part, what makes us, US...granted, it seems stupid to fight amongst ourselves, but consider it in the context of friendly sparring...sometimes low blows are landed but we ARE all on the same server and I want to believe that every single person who posts here wants to make it better, otherwise they wouldn't bother to bitch.<br>
<br>
Yes, the posts are acrimonious.  Yes, they can be hurtful.  Yes, they are filled with badly-argued Ad Hominem attacks, but that is merely lack of polished technique as far as I am concerned.<br>
<br>
So Rant On...when I see a topic about FnF or Reso...I know it's not my problem yet so I just bleep right over it.<br>
<br>
But I read the scams very carefully, because it is &quot;THOSE KINDS&quot; of people and D00ds who can ruin this server faster than anything, in my honest opinion.<br>
<br>
But that's all it is.  An opinion.  And here is where I express it.<br>
<br>
Thank you.<br>
